name: FRIDAY PRAYER the 4th
description:
Celebration of the holiday symbol belonging to the western world which has been known for peace, togetherness, warmth with loved ones. At least that's what it's trying to keep broadcasting and we're keeping an eye on it, some people might disagree. There are various ways of the devil to eliminate that spirit, but I believe humanity will always win.

Merry Christmas, my brothers and sisters.

schedule: mint on friday, burn on next thursday
